66 Qt::ItemFlags JMGItemModel::flags(const QModelIndex& index) const
67 {
68  if (!index.isValid())
69  return Qt::ItemFlags();
70 
71  Qt::ItemFlags f = QAbstractTableModel::flags(index);
72 
73  const moveit::core::JointModel* jm = getJointModel(index);
74  bool is_editable = !jm->isPassive() && !jm->getMimic();
75  f.setFlag(Qt::ItemIsEnabled, is_editable);
76  if (index.column() == 1)
77  f.setFlag(Qt::ItemIsEditable, is_editable);
78  return f;
79 }

81 QVariant JMGItemModel::data(const QModelIndex& index, int role) const
82 {
83  if (!index.isValid())
84  return QVariant();
85 
86  int idx = jmg_ ? jmg_->getVariableIndexList()[index.row()] : index.row();
87  switch (index.column())
88  {
89  case 0: // joint name column
90  switch (role)
91  {
92  case Qt::DisplayRole:
93  return QString::fromStdString(robot_state_.getVariableNames()[idx]);
94  case Qt::TextAlignmentRole:
95  return Qt::AlignLeft;
96  }
97  break;
98  case 1: // joint value column
99  {
100  double value = robot_state_.getVariablePosition(idx);
101  const moveit::core::JointModel* jm = robot_state_.getRobotModel()->getJointOfVariable(idx);
102  switch (role)
103  {
104  case Qt::DisplayRole:
105  return value;
106  case Qt::EditRole:
107  if (jm)
108  return jm->getType() == moveit::core::JointModel::REVOLUTE ? value * 180 / M_PI : value;
109  break;
110  case ProgressBarDelegate::JointTypeRole:
111  if (jm)
112  return jm->getType();
113  break;
114  case ProgressBarDelegate::VariableBoundsRole:
115  if (const moveit::core::VariableBounds* bounds = getVariableBounds(jm, index))
116  return QPointF(bounds->min_position_, bounds->max_position_);
117  break;
118  case Qt::TextAlignmentRole:
119  return Qt::AlignLeft;
120  }
121  }
122  }
123  return QVariant();
124 }

133 bool JMGItemModel::setData(const QModelIndex& index, const QVariant& value, int role)
134 {
135  if (index.column() != 1 || role != Qt::EditRole)
136  return false;
137 
138  int var_idx = jmg_ ? jmg_->getVariableIndexList()[index.row()] : index.row();
139  const moveit::core::JointModel* jm = robot_state_.getRobotModel()->getJointOfVariable(var_idx);
140  if (!value.canConvert<double>())
141  return false;
142 
143  bool ok;
144  double v = value.toDouble(&ok);
145  if (!ok)
146  return false;
147 
148  // for revolute joints, we convert degrees to radians
149  if (jm && jm->getType() == moveit::core::JointModel::REVOLUTE)
150  v *= M_PI / 180;
151 
152  robot_state_.setVariablePosition(var_idx, v);
153  jm->enforcePositionBounds(robot_state_.getVariablePositions() + jm->getFirstVariableIndex());
154  dataChanged(index, index);
155  return true;
156 }

158 const moveit::core::JointModel* JMGItemModel::getJointModel(const QModelIndex& index) const
159 {
160  if (!index.isValid())
161  return nullptr;
162  int var_idx = jmg_ ? jmg_->getVariableIndexList()[index.row()] : index.row();
163  return robot_state_.getRobotModel()->getJointOfVariable(var_idx);

166 const moveit::core::VariableBounds* JMGItemModel::getVariableBounds(const moveit::core::JointModel* jm,
167  const QModelIndex& index) const
168 {
169  if (!jm)
170  return nullptr;
171  int var_idx = jmg_ ? jmg_->getVariableIndexList()[index.row()] : index.row();
172  const moveit::core::VariableBounds* bounds = &jm->getVariableBounds()[var_idx - jm->getFirstVariableIndex()];
173  return bounds->position_bounded_ ? bounds : nullptr;
174 }

201 void MotionPlanningFrameJointsWidget::changePlanningGroup(
202  const std::string& group_name, const robot_interaction::InteractionHandlerPtr& start_state_handler,
203  const robot_interaction::InteractionHandlerPtr& goal_state_handler)
204 {
205  // release previous models (if any)
206  ui_->joints_view_->setModel(nullptr);
207  start_state_model_.reset();
208  goal_state_model_.reset();
209 
210  // create new models
211  start_state_handler_ = start_state_handler;
212  goal_state_handler_ = goal_state_handler;
213  start_state_model_ = std::make_unique<JMGItemModel>(*start_state_handler_->getState(), group_name, this);
214  goal_state_model_ = std::make_unique<JMGItemModel>(*goal_state_handler_->getState(), group_name, this);
215 
216  // forward model updates to the PlanningDisplay
217  connect(start_state_model_.get(), &JMGItemModel::dataChanged, this, [this]() {
218  if (!ignore_state_changes_)
219  planning_display_->setQueryStartState(start_state_model_->getRobotState());
220  });
221  connect(goal_state_model_.get(), &JMGItemModel::dataChanged, this, [this]() {
222  if (!ignore_state_changes_)
223  planning_display_->setQueryGoalState(goal_state_model_->getRobotState());
224  });
225 
226  // show the goal state by default
227  setActiveModel(goal_state_model_.get());
228  updateNullspaceSliders();
229 }

268 // Find matching key vector in columns of haystack and return the best-aligned column index.
269 // Only consider available indexes (> 0). If no match is found, return largest available index.
270 // sign becomes -1 if key has changed sign compared to the matching haystack column.
271 static Eigen::Index findMatching(const Eigen::VectorXd& key, const Eigen::MatrixXd& haystack,
272  const Eigen::VectorXi& available, double& sign)
273 {
274  Eigen::Index result = available.array().maxCoeff();
275  double best_match = 0.0;
276  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < available.rows(); ++i)
277  {
278  int index = available[i];
279  if (index < 0) // index already taken
280  continue;
281  if (index >= haystack.cols())
282  return result;
283  double match = haystack.col(available[i]).transpose() * key;
284  double abs_match = std::abs(match);
285  if (abs_match > 0.5 && abs_match > best_match)
286  {
287  best_match = abs_match;
288  result = index;
289  sign = match > 0 ? 1.0 : -1.0;
290  }
291  }
292  return result;
293 }

295 void MotionPlanningFrameJointsWidget::updateNullspaceSliders()
296 {
297  JMGItemModel* model = dynamic_cast<JMGItemModel*>(ui_->joints_view_->model());
298  std::size_t i = 0;
299  if (model && model->getJointModelGroup() && model->getJointModelGroup()->isChain())
300  {
301  model->getRobotState().updateLinkTransforms();
302  Eigen::MatrixXd jacobian;
303  if (!model->getRobotState().getJacobian(model->getJointModelGroup(),
304  model->getJointModelGroup()->getLinkModels().back(),
305  Eigen::Vector3d::Zero(), jacobian, false))
306  goto cleanup;
307 
308  svd_.compute(jacobian, Eigen::ComputeFullV);
309  Eigen::Index rank = svd_.rank();
310  std::size_t ns_dim = svd_.cols() - rank;
311  Eigen::MatrixXd ns(svd_.cols(), ns_dim);
312  Eigen::VectorXi available(ns_dim);
313  for (std::size_t j = 0; j < ns_dim; ++j)
314  available[j] = j;
315 
316  ns_sliders_.reserve(ns_dim);
317  // create/unhide sliders
318  for (; i < ns_dim; ++i)
319  {
320  if (i >= ns_sliders_.size())
321  ns_sliders_.push_back(createNSSlider(i + 1));
322  ns_sliders_[i]->show();
323 
324  // Find matching null-space basis vector in previous nullspace_
325  double sign = 1.0;
326  const Eigen::VectorXd& current = svd_.matrixV().col(rank + i);
327  Eigen::Index index = findMatching(current, nullspace_, available, sign);
328  ns.col(index).noalias() = sign * current;
329  available[index] = -1; // mark index as taken
330  }
331  nullspace_ = ns;
332  }
333 
334 cleanup:
335  if (i == 0)
336  nullspace_.resize(0, 0);
337 
338  // hide remaining sliders
339  for (; i < ns_sliders_.size(); ++i)
340  ns_sliders_[i]->hide();
341 }

343 QSlider* MotionPlanningFrameJointsWidget::createNSSlider(int i)
344 {
345  JogSlider* slider = new JogSlider(this);
346  slider->setOrientation(Qt::Horizontal);
347  slider->setMaximum(0.1);
348  slider->setToolTip(QString("Nullspace dim #%1").arg(i));
349  ui_->nullspace_layout_->addWidget(slider);
350  connect(slider, SIGNAL(triggered(double)), this, SLOT(jogNullspace(double)));
351  return slider;
352 }
353 
354 void MotionPlanningFrameJointsWidget::jogNullspace(double value)
355 {
356  if (value == 0)
357  return;
358 
359  std::size_t index = std::find(ns_sliders_.begin(), ns_sliders_.end(), sender()) - ns_sliders_.begin();
360  if (static_cast<int>(index) >= nullspace_.cols())
361  return;
362 
363  JMGItemModel* model = dynamic_cast<JMGItemModel*>(ui_->joints_view_->model());
364  if (!model)
365  return;
366 
367  Eigen::VectorXd values;
368  model->getRobotState().copyJointGroupPositions(model->getJointModelGroup(), values);
369  values += value * nullspace_.col(index);
370  model->getRobotState().setJointGroupPositions(model->getJointModelGroup(), values);
371  model->getRobotState().harmonizePositions(model->getJointModelGroup());
372  triggerUpdate(model);
373 }

375 void ProgressBarDelegate::paint(QPainter* painter, const QStyleOptionViewItem& option, const QModelIndex& index) const
376 {
377  // copied from QStyledItemDelegate::paint
378  QStyle* style = option.widget ? option.widget->style() : QApplication::style();
379  QStyleOptionViewItem style_option = option;
380  initStyleOption(&style_option, index);
381 
382  if (index.column() == 1)
383  {
384  QVariant joint_type = index.data(JointTypeRole);
385  double value = index.data().toDouble();
386  if (joint_type.isValid())
387  {
388  switch (joint_type.toInt())
389  {
390  case moveit::core::JointModel::REVOLUTE:
391  style_option.text = option.locale.toString(value * 180 / M_PI, 'f', 0).append("");
392  break;
393  case moveit::core::JointModel::PRISMATIC:
394  style_option.text = option.locale.toString(value, 'f', 3).append("m");
395  break;
396  default:
397  break;
398  }
399  }
400 
401  QVariant vbounds = index.data(VariableBoundsRole);
402  if (vbounds.isValid())
403  {
404  QPointF bounds = vbounds.toPointF();
405  const float min = bounds.x();
406  const float max = bounds.y();
407 
408  QStyleOptionProgressBar opt;
409  opt.rect = option.rect;
410  opt.minimum = 0;
411  opt.maximum = 1000;
412  opt.progress = 1000. * (value - min) / (max - min);
413  opt.text = style_option.text;
414  opt.textAlignment = style_option.displayAlignment;
415  opt.textVisible = true;
416  style->drawControl(QStyle::CE_ProgressBar, &opt, painter);
417  return;
418  }
419  }
420 
421  style->drawControl(QStyle::CE_ItemViewItem, &style_option, painter, option.widget);
422 }

424 QWidget* ProgressBarDelegate::createEditor(QWidget* parent, const QStyleOptionViewItem& option,
425  const QModelIndex& index) const
426 
427 {
428  if (index.column() == 1)
429  {
430  QVariant vbounds = index.data(VariableBoundsRole);
431  if (vbounds.isValid())
432  {
433  QPointF bounds = vbounds.toPointF();
434  float min = bounds.x();
435  float max = bounds.y();
436  bool is_revolute = (index.data(JointTypeRole).toInt() == moveit::core::JointModel::REVOLUTE);
437  if (is_revolute)
438  {
439  min *= 180. / M_PI;
440  max *= 180. / M_PI;
441  }
442  auto* editor = new ProgressBarEditor(parent, min, max, is_revolute ? 0 : 3);
443  connect(editor, &ProgressBarEditor::editingFinished, this, &ProgressBarDelegate::commitAndCloseEditor);
444  connect(editor, &ProgressBarEditor::valueChanged, this, [=](float value) {
445  const_cast<QAbstractItemModel*>(index.model())->setData(index, value, Qt::EditRole);
446  });
447  return editor;
448  }
449  }
450  return QStyledItemDelegate::createEditor(parent, option, index);
451 }

464 bool JointsWidgetEventFilter::eventFilter(QObject* /*target*/, QEvent* event)
465 {
466  if (event->type() == QEvent::MouseButtonPress)
467  {
468  QAbstractItemView* view = qobject_cast<QAbstractItemView*>(parent());
469  QModelIndex index = view->indexAt(static_cast<QMouseEvent*>(event)->pos());
470  if (index.flags() & Qt::ItemIsEditable) // mouse event on any editable slider?
471  {
472  view->setCurrentIndex(index);
473  view->edit(index);
474  return true; // event handled
475  }
476  }
477  return false;
478 }

488 void ProgressBarEditor::paintEvent(QPaintEvent* /*event*/)
489 {
490  QPainter painter(this);
491 
492  QStyleOptionProgressBar opt;
493  opt.rect = rect();
494  opt.palette = this->palette();
495  opt.minimum = 0;
496  opt.maximum = 1000;
497  opt.progress = 1000. * (value_ - min_) / (max_ - min_);
498  opt.text = QLocale().toString(value_, 'f', digits_);

510 void ProgressBarEditor::mouseMoveEvent(QMouseEvent* event)
511 {
512  float v = std::min(max_, std::max(min_, min_ + event->x() * (max_ - min_) / width()));
513  if (value_ != v)
514  {
515  value_ = v;
516  valueChanged(v);
517  update();
518  }
519  event->accept();
520 }
